‘Translating Emotions’ SERIES (SEASON 3 - DUCT TAPE)
The creator attempts to express and immortalize his emotions thru art. Interpreting emojis on his digital portraits. 



---------------
Collecting this and other 1/1s creation means supporting a dream of the artist to continue his craft while making a living.
Join Jakestudyos on his journey and evolution.


UPDATE: I'm on the way to get some upgrades to my digital tools. Thank you for the rightful collectors and believers.  Love you all.
